Subject: Lost ability to access reporting site
Description: We updated to Netwrix Enterprise Auditor this morning and this afternoon we found we no longer have access to the reporting site that was previously on port 8082.
Solution_Comment__c:
Issue
Published Reports Web Console was inaccessible.
Cause
Service Log On As name was set to Local System instead of Service Account

Resolution
Changed services log on as name to macth the service account being used for the AIC
